quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  33,55,"Shini tsimbi khubo (abakhasi) okhulolana nende basabwe tawe, nohomba Abana babu beshisiani, nohomba Abasiani babu, nohomba Abana babasiani babu, nohomba Abana babakhana babu, nohomba Abakhasi shinga bo, nohomba balia abemikhono chiabu emilunji chiatila, ne rie Nyasaye. Toto Nyasaye ni Omuloli muno wabuli eshindu."
  33,56,"Toto Nyasaye nende Abamalaika bebe basabilanga Omurumwa (tsimbabaasi). Enywe abasuubila, musabile (Omurumwa) ne mushesie omulembe muno."
  33,57,"Toto balia basinyisinjia Nyasaye nende Omurumwa wuwe, Nyasaye abatsuba khushialo nende mwikulu, ne yabarecheshela eshinyasio (shietsisoni) shokhututuyia."
  33,58,"Ne balia basinyisinjia Abasuubili Abasatsa nende Abasuubili Abakhasi khukabalakholele tawe, toto bamala okhuchinga obuchishi obukhongo nende tsimbii tsilolekha."
  33,59,"Ewe Omurumwa, boolela Abakhasi bao, nende Abakhana bao, nende Abakhasi babasuubili, beishiliekhwo obulayi tsingubo tsiabu, okhukhola endio khulachila bamanyishe, kho balasinyisibwa tawe, ne Nyasaye ni Omulesheli muno, Owetsimbabaasi po."
  33,60,"Ne Abeshikhabili nende balia bali nende obulwale mumioyo chiabu, nende balia abasalasinjia obubii mulukongo, nibalalekha tawe, toto khwitsa okhubasasiakhwo ewe, ne shibetsa okhwikhala omo ahambi ninawe tawe halali khubise bititi butswa."
  33,61,"Bali nende eshilamo. Wosiwosi wabalolekhana, batilwe mana berwe okhwirwa khwatoto."
  33,62,"Eyo niimero ya Nyasaye khubalia baraanjilila. Ne sholinyoolela imero ya Nyasaye obukalukhani tawe."